title: Image Hosting Sites
description:
[imagebin.ca](https://imagebin.ca)
Upload to imagebin.ca through the command line:
```bash
curl -F file="@/path/to/file.png" https://imagebin.ca/upload.php
```
[filebin.net](https://filebin.net)
Upload to filebin.net through the command line:
```bash
curl --data-binary "@/path/to/file.png" -H "filename: file.png" https://filebin.net
```
